sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Nurse
    participant UI as React SPA
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant SVC as AdmissionService
    participant G as LangGraph Orchestrator
    participant T as Triage Agent
    participant D as Disease Forecast Agent
    participant B as Bed Allocation Agent
    participant P as Parallel Agents
    participant C as Carbon Agent
    participant E as Executive Agent
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant WS as WebSocket Hub

    Nurse->>UI: Enter arrival + vitals
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/admissions/arrival
    API->>SVC: create_arrival(payload)
    SVC->>DB: insert admissions (status=triaged)
    SVC->>G: invoke(trigger=patient_arrival)

    G->>DB: read hospital snapshot
    DB-->>G: snapshot

    G->>T: analyse(state)
    T->>T: XGBoost ESI + red-flag rules
    T->>T: Gemini rationale
    T-->>G: TriageResult(esi, dept, rationale)

    G->>D: analyse(state)
    D-->>G: DiseaseForecastResult(14d admissions, ICU demand)

    G->>B: analyse(state)
    B->>B: score candidate beds, predict LOS
    alt ICU occupancy >= 90%
        B-->>G: escalate ICU overflow
    else capacity available
        B-->>G: BedAllocationResult(bed_id, LOS)
    end

    par Parallel fan-out
        G->>P: medicine.analyse
    and
        G->>P: energy.analyse
    and
        G->>P: water.analyse
    and
        G->>P: waste.analyse
    and
        G->>P: dispatch.analyse
    end
    P-->>G: five AgentResults

    G->>C: analyse(state)
    C-->>G: CarbonResult(scopes, score)

    G->>G: conflict_resolver
    G->>E: analyse(state)
    E->>E: CrewAI executive crew
    E-->>G: ExecutiveResult(summary, action plan)

    G->>DB: write agent_logs, notifications, reservations
    G-->>SVC: HealMatrixState
    SVC-->>API: AdmissionResponse
    API-->>UI: 201 Created
    G->>WS: publish notification
    WS-->>UI: live alert
    UI-->>Nurse: Bed 3B assigned, ESI 2, rationale shown
